  "page": "A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics</b></i> is an upcoming tabletop skirmish game produced by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CMON_Limited\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:CMON Limited\">CMON Limited</a> and Dark Swords Miniatures, based on the <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> novels by <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The first Skirmish Set, <i>Battle of the Trident</i>, will be published in 2025.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire:_Tactics&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><span class=\"citation web\">García,&#32;Elio&#32;(February 22, 2024).&#32;<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/News/Entry/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Tactics_Game_Nearing_End_of_Fundraising\">\"A Song of Ice and Fire: Tactics Game Nearing End of Fundraising\"</a>.&#32;Westeros.org<span class=\"printonly\">.&#32;<a class=\"external free\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/News/Entry/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Tactics_Game_Nearing_End_of_Fundraising\">https://www.westeros.org/News/Entry/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire_Tactics_Game_Nearing_End_of_Fundraising</a></span>.</s